556
00:25:21,591 --> 00:25:23,740
(My company requires me to work
12 hours a day for six days a week.)

557
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:24,540
(I want to resign,)

558
00:25:24,540 --> 00:25:25,940
(but I can't muster up the courage)

559
00:25:25,940 --> 00:25:27,860
(because of financial stress.)

560
00:25:27,860 --> 00:25:29,380
(I don't want money.)

561
00:25:29,380 --> 00:25:31,460
(I just want you to help me)

562
00:25:31,460 --> 00:25:33,460
(get a job at Tengda Games.)

563
00:25:33,460 --> 00:25:34,940
(Thank you.)

564
00:25:34,940 --> 00:25:36,300
(If this is difficult,)

565
00:25:36,300 --> 00:25:37,740
(you can also transfer money to me.)

566
00:25:37,820 --> 00:25:40,100
(No, it's like this.)

567
00:25:40,100 --> 00:25:40,940
(Mister,)

568
00:25:40,940 --> 00:25:41,940
(Tengda has)

569
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,620
(a hiring standard.)

570
00:25:43,635 --> 00:25:45,740
(Mr. Ma, what's the standard?)
(Backdoors are not allowed.)

571
00:25:45,740 --> 00:25:46,700
(No backdoors.)

572
00:25:46,700 --> 00:25:47,460
(However,)

573
00:25:47,460 --> 00:25:50,420
(I will still help you out a little.)

574
00:25:50,580 --> 00:25:51,500
(Please wait.)

575
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:52,620
(Calm down.)

576
00:25:53,460 --> 00:25:54,460
(I'll help you)

577
00:25:54,460 --> 00:25:57,340
(quit and fulfill your dream bravely.)

578
00:25:58,180 --> 00:25:59,660
(Look over here.)

579
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,380
(I transferred 10,000 yuan to you.)

580
00:26:01,380 --> 00:26:02,860
(I wish for your success.)

581
00:26:05,580 --> 00:26:07,540
You gave him 10,000 yuan?

582
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:08,220
Yes.

583
00:26:08,860 --> 00:26:09,860
Don't worry, Qian.

584
00:26:09,860 --> 00:26:11,380
I used my own money.

585
00:26:11,380 --> 00:26:12,540
DreamForge and Tengda Games

586
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:13,900
paid me so much every month anyway.

587
00:26:13,902 --> 00:26:14,968
I can't even spend it all.

588
00:26:15,180 --> 00:26:16,180
Enough, Ma.

589
00:26:17,340 --> 00:26:18,389
Stop telling me

590
00:26:18,390 --> 00:26:19,860
that you can't spend all your salary.

591
00:26:19,860 --> 00:26:21,060
Keep it yourself.

592
00:26:21,060 --> 00:26:21,700
Sure.

593
00:26:21,940 --> 00:26:22,300
Qian,

594
00:26:22,300 --> 00:26:24,013
can I propose this project
on the agenda?

595
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,060
I quite like it.

596
00:26:26,300 --> 00:26:27,660
If I don't do it,

597
00:26:27,660 --> 00:26:28,300
are you planning

598
00:26:28,300 --> 00:26:29,900
to keep using your money?

599
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:30,620
Yes.

600
00:26:30,780 --> 00:26:31,900
This is so meaningful.

601
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:33,100
I don't plan to stop.

602
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:35,502
In that case, it's better
if Tengda supports you.

603
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:38,100
Qian, come on. Give me a hug.

604
00:26:38,100 --> 00:26:38,740
It's time.

605
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:40,500
Qian, it's time to give me a hug.

606
00:26:40,500 --> 00:26:41,340
Qian.

607
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:46,300
Mr. Pei.

608
00:26:47,780 --> 00:26:49,100
Use it.

609
00:26:49,100 --> 00:26:50,180
I'm leaving.

610
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:50,740
Sure.

611
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:16,660
(Hello, Mr. Ma.)

612
00:27:16,746 --> 00:27:19,257
(Dreams Fulfilled Immediately)
(I'm the boss of a small company.)

613
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:21,540
(However, due to
my company's poor operation,)

614
00:27:21,540 --> 00:27:23,700
(I only get paid 5,000 yuan a month.)

615
00:27:23,700 --> 00:27:25,740
(I want to buy my friend a gift.)

616
00:27:25,740 --> 00:27:26,940
(I need 8,000 yuan)

617
00:27:26,940 --> 00:27:28,580
(but I don't have money.)

618
00:27:28,780 --> 00:27:30,940
(Can you help me fulfill this wish?)

619
00:27:40,540 --> 00:27:43,220
It feels great to leech off Ma Yang.

620
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:46,340
(Transfer Details)

621
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:50,100
Seriously? He transfers money
to help people fulfill their dreams?

622
00:27:50,100 --> 00:27:51,420
It must be a scam.

623
00:27:53,124 --> 00:27:54,100
It's already trending.

624
00:27:54,100 --> 00:27:55,124
I think it should be true.

625
00:27:55,146 --> 00:27:55,700
Whatever.

626
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:57,570
Let's see
if he can help us pay for this meal.

627
00:27:58,220 --> 00:27:59,780
I really got 56 yuan.

628
00:27:59,780 --> 00:28:01,140
These two cups of coffee are free.

629
00:28:02,820 --> 00:28:03,900
Let me try it again.

630
00:28:05,180 --> 00:28:06,980
Only one opportunity for one account?

631
00:28:06,980 --> 00:28:08,460
Try it again with a new account.

632
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:20,980
(Ma Yang)

633
00:28:22,020 --> 00:28:23,540
Mr. Ma did transfer money to me.

634
00:28:26,780 --> 00:28:27,820
Mr. Qiao.

635
00:28:28,340 --> 00:28:29,460
I knew it.

636
00:28:29,460 --> 00:28:31,591
The profile picture
of Aluminium Alloy Materials Q

637
00:28:31,591 --> 00:28:32,480
looked familiar.

638
00:28:32,502 --> 00:28:33,740
When I checked the account,

639
00:28:33,740 --> 00:28:35,768
the posts were all about
how handsome Mr. Qiao is.

640
00:28:35,768 --> 00:28:37,260
It's obviously your sub-account.

641
00:28:37,500 --> 00:28:38,060
However,

642
00:28:38,060 --> 00:28:39,220
I've still decided

643
00:28:39,220 --> 00:28:40,620
to let you leech off me once.

644
00:28:40,620 --> 00:28:42,780
Keep praising Tengda Games
in the future.

645
00:28:44,820 --> 00:28:47,100
Mr. Ma, you found me.

646
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:48,420
It's me indeed.

647
00:28:49,180 --> 00:28:50,180
Don't worry, Mr. Ma.

648
00:28:50,780 --> 00:28:52,580
If you launch a new game in the future,

649
00:28:52,780 --> 00:28:53,900
I've decided

650
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:55,580
to fully support it.

651
00:28:59,740 --> 00:29:01,540
Qian knows me best.

652
00:29:42,180 --> 00:29:44,740
After speaking with you,

653
00:29:44,740 --> 00:29:45,820
we've improved

654
00:29:45,820 --> 00:29:47,660
The Divine Mountains and Seas
once again.

655
00:29:47,940 --> 00:29:49,740
Right now, development is going well.

656
00:29:50,060 --> 00:29:52,260
However, a few parts

657
00:29:52,260 --> 00:29:53,100
require extra budget.

658
00:29:53,100 --> 00:29:54,380
I want to confirm it with you.

659
00:29:54,380 --> 00:29:55,140
About this,

660
00:29:55,140 --> 00:29:57,100
the project team
can just decide on its own.

661
00:29:57,100 --> 00:29:57,980
Just do it.

662
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:59,260
There's no cap on the budget.

663
00:30:00,780 --> 00:30:01,780
Thank you, Mr. Pei.

664
00:30:01,780 --> 00:30:02,300
Oh,

665
00:30:02,300 --> 00:30:04,460
I also want to tell you
about the other games' update.

666
00:30:04,780 --> 00:30:06,340
Although you said

667
00:30:06,340 --> 00:30:08,660
we don't need
to update our previous games,

668
00:30:08,980 --> 00:30:12,300
we still think it's a pity
not to give them updates.

669
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:13,140
Well,

670
00:30:13,140 --> 00:30:15,140
I did say that before.

671
00:30:15,387 --> 00:30:16,027
Well,

672
00:30:16,180 --> 00:30:17,220
you'll be in charge

673
00:30:17,220 --> 00:30:18,740
of all these games from now on.

674
00:30:18,740 --> 00:30:19,940
If you have any ideas,

675
00:30:19,940 --> 00:30:20,980
just update the games

676
00:30:20,980 --> 00:30:22,340
when you feel like it.

677
00:30:24,060 --> 00:30:24,580
All right.

678
00:30:29,300 --> 00:30:30,100
By the way,

679
00:30:30,100 --> 00:30:30,940
Lin Wan...

680
00:30:31,580 --> 00:30:32,620
Well...

681
00:30:32,620 --> 00:30:35,540
Didn't you tell
the designated driver company

682
00:30:35,540 --> 00:30:37,060
to hire me for a month?

683
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:41,220
I took the job since I can make
more money than usual

684
00:30:41,220 --> 00:30:43,940
but I realized
you are not here as a passenger.

685
00:30:43,940 --> 00:30:46,420
You are sitting in the passenger seat
to discuss work with me.

686
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:49,100
You've been working hard enough at work.

687
00:30:49,300 --> 00:30:50,940
Now, you still want me to work two jobs.

688
00:30:51,700 --> 00:30:53,380
This job is not worth it at all.

689
00:30:54,820 --> 00:30:57,340
Mr. Pei, do you care about
the money you make working this job?

690
00:30:57,340 --> 00:30:59,260
Didn't you say
you were experiencing life?

691
00:30:59,580 --> 00:31:00,100
I...

692
00:31:00,540 --> 00:31:01,900
I am

693
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:04,020
always serious,

694
00:31:04,020 --> 00:31:05,380
no matter what I do.

695
00:31:05,380 --> 00:31:05,900
Look.

696
00:31:06,020 --> 00:31:06,860
I have the resolve

697
00:31:06,860 --> 00:31:08,460
to be a designated driver.

698
00:31:08,580 --> 00:31:10,009
The time I use and the money I make

699
00:31:10,010 --> 00:31:10,940
as a designated driver

700
00:31:10,940 --> 00:31:12,413
are very important to me right now.

701
00:31:14,540 --> 00:31:16,540
Mr. Pei, your attitude

702
00:31:16,540 --> 00:31:18,740
of being immersed in your role

703
00:31:19,020 --> 00:31:20,420
is indeed impressive.

704
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:22,700
No wonder you can make such good games.

705
00:31:23,500 --> 00:31:24,540
Now that I think about it,

706
00:31:24,780 --> 00:31:27,780
I should improve on the immersiveness
of The Divine Mountains and Seas.

707
00:31:29,502 --> 00:31:31,060
Lin Wan, help me answer the phone.

708
00:31:31,580 --> 00:31:32,180
Sure.

709
00:31:33,820 --> 00:31:34,500
Hello.

710
00:31:34,500 --> 00:31:36,100
Hello, are you Mr. Pei?

711
00:31:36,460 --> 00:31:38,540
We noticed you have a loan record.

712
00:31:38,660 --> 00:31:39,660
We have a small...

713
00:31:41,740 --> 00:31:43,300
Mr. Pei, you got a loan?

714
00:31:43,300 --> 00:31:44,540
Is it because of Tengda?

715
00:31:47,060 --> 00:31:48,260
Loan?

716
00:31:48,300 --> 00:31:50,020
I'll never get a loan.

717
00:31:50,020 --> 00:31:51,340
This is

718
00:31:51,980 --> 00:31:53,180
an obvious

719
00:31:54,260 --> 00:31:55,260
harassment call.

720
00:32:02,940 --> 00:32:03,620
Well,

721
00:32:04,780 --> 00:32:05,460
Lin Wan,

722
00:32:05,820 --> 00:32:06,780
can you

723
00:32:07,180 --> 00:32:09,380
tell the designated driver company

724
00:32:10,580 --> 00:32:11,500
and say

725
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:13,460
you're going to cancel
my month-long hire?

726
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:14,900
Right now,

727
00:32:14,900 --> 00:32:16,540
I really can't work for you alone.

728
00:32:16,540 --> 00:32:18,235
I must only work more,
so I get paid more.

729
00:32:19,060 --> 00:32:20,900
Only by doing this can I

730
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:22,780
experience life better.

731
00:32:23,020 --> 00:32:23,780
Don't worry.

732
00:32:23,780 --> 00:32:24,820
I completely trust you

733
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:26,580
when it comes to games.

734
00:32:26,580 --> 00:32:27,300
I support you.

735
00:32:27,300 --> 00:32:28,300
I believe you can

736
00:32:28,300 --> 00:32:29,900
do better and greater,

737
00:32:29,900 --> 00:32:31,740
leading Tengda Games to greater glory.

738
00:32:34,260 --> 00:32:34,860
All right.

739
00:32:35,220 --> 00:32:36,180
I'll call

740
00:32:36,180 --> 00:32:37,630
the designated driver company later.

741
00:32:37,940 --> 00:32:38,940
Thank you.

742
00:32:54,380 --> 00:32:55,220
Mr. Li Jr.

743
00:32:55,580 --> 00:32:56,460
This time,

744
00:32:56,780 --> 00:32:58,900
I came to Jinchuan on purpose

745
00:32:58,900 --> 00:33:01,220
to bring you good news.

746
00:33:01,502 --> 00:33:03,660
Development and production
of Eternal Reincarnation

747
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:04,980
are completed.

748
00:33:04,980 --> 00:33:06,460
It will be launched soon.

749
00:33:07,300 --> 00:33:08,620
Rest assured.

750
00:33:09,420 --> 00:33:11,300
Previously, we've always been surpassed

751
00:33:11,700 --> 00:33:12,540
by Tengda Games.

752
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:14,460
This time, Eternal Reincarnation

753
00:33:14,460 --> 00:33:16,500
will surely crush Pei Qian.

754
00:33:17,220 --> 00:33:17,780
Its sales

755
00:33:17,780 --> 00:33:19,740
will be better than all of his games

756
00:33:19,740 --> 00:33:20,700
combined.

757
00:33:21,300 --> 00:33:22,300
Yes, Mr. Li Jr.

758
00:33:22,300 --> 00:33:23,860
This time, Sky Fire will surely win.

759
00:33:24,100 --> 00:33:24,740
Come on.

760
00:33:24,740 --> 00:33:25,980
Let's have a toast to victory.

761
00:33:25,980 --> 00:33:26,340
Come on.

762
00:33:26,340 --> 00:33:26,900
Cheers.

763
00:33:31,860 --> 00:33:32,900
Mr. Zhou,

764
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,380
you can't say things that way sometimes.

765
00:33:35,980 --> 00:33:38,020
Pei Qian is my friend, after all.

766
00:33:38,020 --> 00:33:38,620
Right?

767
00:33:38,620 --> 00:33:40,900
This is a healthy competition.

768
00:33:40,900 --> 00:33:41,620
Of course,

769
00:33:41,940 --> 00:33:44,020
I'm very happy

770
00:33:44,020 --> 00:33:46,140
if Sky Fire comes on top of this.

771
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:47,380
However,

772
00:33:47,380 --> 00:33:49,860
Tengda Games is indeed capable.

773
00:33:49,860 --> 00:33:50,580
Am I right?

774
00:33:50,580 --> 00:33:51,860
You're...

775
00:33:55,060 --> 00:33:56,060
See?

776
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:57,460
Mr. Li Jr. has a broad perspective.

777
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:58,620
Come, Mr. Li Jr.

778
00:33:58,620 --> 00:33:59,860
Come.

779
00:34:03,900 --> 00:34:04,820
Xuming.

780
00:34:05,220 --> 00:34:07,380
Mr. Li Jr. is almost done.
Call a designated driver.

781
00:34:07,420 --> 00:34:07,820
Sure.

782
00:34:07,820 --> 00:34:08,340
No.

783
00:34:08,500 --> 00:34:09,300
I can still drink.

784
00:34:09,300 --> 00:34:09,980
I'm fine.

785
00:34:09,980 --> 00:34:11,220
I know. You're fine.

786
00:34:11,220 --> 00:34:12,420
Come. Let me drink with you.

787
00:34:16,300 --> 00:34:17,140
Mr. Li Jr.,

788
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:18,300
well,

789
00:34:18,300 --> 00:34:19,700
ask your driver to go home.

790
00:34:19,700 --> 00:34:20,857
I'll drive you back later.

791
00:34:20,924 --> 00:34:22,660
We can also chat alone

792
00:34:22,660 --> 00:34:23,900
on our way back.

793
00:34:25,780 --> 00:34:26,740
Mr. Zhou,

794
00:34:27,340 --> 00:34:28,460
you need something?

795
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:32,180
The person who understands me best

796
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:33,300
is indeed Mr. Li Jr.

797
00:34:33,324 --> 00:34:34,020
All right. Cheers.

798
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:34,780
Cheers.

799
00:34:39,100 --> 00:34:40,420
Have a little more.

800
00:34:40,860 --> 00:34:41,420
Here you go.

801
00:34:46,300 --> 00:34:48,340
I still need to work harder.

802
00:34:48,340 --> 00:34:50,500
Every job counts.

803
00:34:52,146 --> 00:34:54,340
Didn't they say it's easier
to get more jobs at night?

804
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,420
Why haven't I seen any?

805
00:34:55,980 --> 00:34:58,500
(You have a new job.
Please attend to it immediately.)

806
00:34:58,820 --> 00:34:59,740
Get it.

807
00:35:01,863 --> 00:35:04,223
Oh my.
The registration plate is awesome.

808
00:35:04,580 --> 00:35:05,540
There's even a tip.

809
00:35:05,540 --> 00:35:07,300
(Driver, are you coming?)

810
00:35:07,300 --> 00:35:08,460
Don't worry, Sir.

811
00:35:08,860 --> 00:35:11,180
Designated Driver P will be here soon.

812
00:35:20,100 --> 00:35:20,860
Sir.

813
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:22,220
Designated Driver, where are you?

814
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:23,435
I've been waiting for so long.

815
00:35:23,460 --> 00:35:24,220
Sir,

816
00:35:24,220 --> 00:35:25,860
I'll reach the entrance soon.

817
00:35:25,860 --> 00:35:27,140
It's two of you, right?

818
00:35:27,740 --> 00:35:28,900
You're at the entrance?

819
00:35:29,220 --> 00:35:29,980
I don't see you.

820
00:35:29,980 --> 00:35:30,900
Where are you?

821
00:35:31,460 --> 00:35:33,140
Didn't I tip you just now?

822
00:35:33,140 --> 00:35:33,780
I'm telling you.

823
00:35:33,780 --> 00:35:34,780
If you don't come here,

824
00:35:35,060 --> 00:35:36,500
I'll cancel my tip and report you.

825
00:35:36,500 --> 00:35:37,500
Hurry up!

826
00:35:38,340 --> 00:35:39,700
Zhou Muyan?

827
00:35:47,220 --> 00:35:48,140
Do you need something?

828
00:35:49,380 --> 00:35:49,860
Mr. Li Jr.

829
00:35:49,860 --> 00:35:50,780
Wait for a while.

830
00:35:50,780 --> 00:35:51,980
He'll be here soon.

831
00:35:52,500 --> 00:35:53,380
If he isn't,

832
00:35:53,540 --> 00:35:54,700
I'll make a complaint.

833
00:35:54,746 --> 00:35:55,880
(Professional Designated Driver)
Here he is.

834
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,380
Sir, I'm glad to serve.

835
00:35:57,380 --> 00:35:59,524
Why are you so slow
after receiving a tip? Let's go.

836
00:35:59,980 --> 00:36:00,900
Wait!

837
00:36:01,791 --> 00:36:02,620
Something's wrong.

838
00:36:02,620 --> 00:36:03,420
Look! He's wearing...

839
00:36:03,420 --> 00:36:04,980
There's no problem. Get on.

840
00:36:04,980 --> 00:36:06,740
Sir, can you open the trunk?

841
00:36:06,740 --> 00:36:07,500
Sure.

842
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:09,080
Didn't you see that he's wearing a mask?

843
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:09,780
Stop!

844
00:36:09,780 --> 00:36:11,020
He's here to rob me.

845
00:36:11,020 --> 00:36:11,420
Mr. Li Jr.

846
00:36:11,420 --> 00:36:12,180
Get in.

847
00:36:12,180 --> 00:36:13,835
I have something important to tell you.

848
00:36:28,380 --> 00:36:29,300
Well...

849
00:36:29,980 --> 00:36:30,660
Mr. Driver...

850
00:36:30,980 --> 00:36:32,740
Are you really wearing this mask

851
00:36:32,740 --> 00:36:34,260
just to drive

852
00:36:34,260 --> 00:36:35,700
and not have any weird ideas?

853
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:41,340
What weird ideas can he have?

854
00:36:41,860 --> 00:36:44,060
Perhaps his face is full of pimples,

855
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:45,435
and he doesn't want us to see him.

856
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:46,500
Forget it.

857
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:48,700
Won't he get more pimples wearing that?

858
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,500
Mr. Li Jr.,

859
00:36:53,940 --> 00:36:56,740
don't always think of others
as bad people.

860
00:36:56,940 --> 00:36:59,420
You might not realize it

861
00:36:59,420 --> 00:37:01,180
if the real bad guy is just beside you.

862
00:37:04,613 --> 00:37:05,900
Who are you talking about?

863
00:37:06,060 --> 00:37:06,980
Who else?

864
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:08,300
Pei Qian.

865
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:10,740
Why do I spend so much money

866
00:37:10,740 --> 00:37:12,420
this time on Eternal Reincarnation?

867
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:14,220
Because I want to knock him out

868
00:37:14,420 --> 00:37:15,940
and let him die a cruel death.

869
00:37:20,140 --> 00:37:21,100
Mr. Zhou.

870
00:37:21,568 --> 00:37:23,020
Just now, there were many people.

871
00:37:23,020 --> 00:37:24,460
I feel bad talking more.

872
00:37:24,980 --> 00:37:26,460
Now, there are only two of us.

873
00:37:26,460 --> 00:37:27,540
Let's talk about this

874
00:37:27,540 --> 00:37:28,980
behind closed doors.

875
00:37:36,220 --> 00:37:36,860
Look.

876
00:37:37,140 --> 00:37:37,820
I think

877
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:39,460
Sky Fire and Tengda Games

878
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:40,740
are having a healthy competition,

879
00:37:40,740 --> 00:37:42,140
so that's a good thing.

880
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:44,780
However, I think you are going overboard

881
00:37:45,235 --> 00:37:47,168
if your actions
are specifically against Mr. Pei.

882
00:37:47,940 --> 00:37:48,420
That's...

883
00:37:48,700 --> 00:37:49,100
No.

884
00:37:49,100 --> 00:37:50,180
You are completely obsessed

885
00:37:50,180 --> 00:37:51,380
with defeating him.

886
00:37:51,380 --> 00:37:53,191
Back then, you hired
people to slander him.

887
00:37:53,300 --> 00:37:55,180
That's wrong.

888
00:37:55,180 --> 00:37:56,820
How am I wrong?

889
00:37:58,260 --> 00:37:58,860
Mr. Li Jr.

890
00:37:58,860 --> 00:37:59,940
You are my investor.

891
00:37:59,940 --> 00:38:01,899
I can turn a blind eye
if you reprimand me a little,

892
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:04,100
but I think you're now siding
with Pei Qian a bit too much.

893
00:38:04,100 --> 00:38:04,980
I heard you moved

894
00:38:04,980 --> 00:38:06,100
to Four Wall Apartments,

895
00:38:06,100 --> 00:38:06,740
right?

896
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:07,780
Is that right?

897
00:38:08,300 --> 00:38:10,500
As the young master of Fuhui,

898
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:12,580
you moved to Tengda's apartment.

899
00:38:12,580 --> 00:38:14,300
What will your father think
when he finds out?

900
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:14,780
No.

901
00:38:14,780 --> 00:38:17,340
You... This is between us.
Why are you getting my dad involved?

902
00:38:17,340 --> 00:38:17,860
Right?

903
00:38:17,860 --> 00:38:18,820
Besides, I'm telling you.

904
00:38:18,820 --> 00:38:19,900
Mr. Pei has

905
00:38:19,900 --> 00:38:21,740
many strengths.

906
00:38:21,740 --> 00:38:22,780
For example,

907
00:38:22,860 --> 00:38:24,460
he is better at me than investing.

908
00:38:24,460 --> 00:38:26,740
He is better than you
at developing games.

909
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:27,700
What's wrong with

910
00:38:27,700 --> 00:38:28,740
being close to him?

911
00:38:28,740 --> 00:38:30,060
It'll only benefit me, right?

912
00:38:30,060 --> 00:38:31,580
How does it benefit you?

913
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:34,140
Do you want to become Pei Qian's lackey?

914
00:38:34,140 --> 00:38:35,660
Or do you want to hand over

915
00:38:35,660 --> 00:38:36,980
Lishi Capital to him?

916
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:37,780
In the end,

917
00:38:37,780 --> 00:38:39,660
both of us will end up

918
00:38:39,660 --> 00:38:40,740
becoming Pei Qian's driver!

919
00:38:40,740 --> 00:38:42,235
Seriously, there's no need to...

920
00:38:44,660 --> 00:38:45,340
Watch out!

921
00:39:21,100 --> 00:39:21,980
Are you mad?

922
00:39:22,391 --> 00:39:23,591
Sorry.

923
00:39:23,591 --> 00:39:26,146
- Do you think apologizing helps?
- Do you think apologizing helps?

924
00:39:26,220 --> 00:39:27,620
What were you doing?

925
00:39:30,380 --> 00:39:31,460
- Pei Qian?
- Pei Qian?

926
00:39:31,940 --> 00:39:32,820
Sorry.

927
00:39:37,140 --> 00:39:37,740
Quick!

928
00:39:38,020 --> 00:39:38,900
Quick!

929
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,900
Catch him! Don't let him escape!

930
00:39:41,380 --> 00:39:43,060
Pei Qian, stop!

931
00:39:44,100 --> 00:39:44,980
Pei Qian!

932
00:39:46,620 --> 00:39:47,620
Mr. Pei!

933
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:48,300
Pei Qian!

934
00:39:48,300 --> 00:39:49,460
It's you, Mr. Pei?

935
00:39:49,620 --> 00:39:50,300
Mr. Pei!

936
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,740
What? Mr. Pei, I...

937
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:57,180
Pei Qian!

938
00:40:00,300 --> 00:40:02,500
Mr. Pei, what's going on?

939
00:40:06,060 --> 00:40:11,900
♪The moonlight kisses the balcony♪

940
00:40:14,780 --> 00:40:20,100
♪The clouds cause trouble for no reason♪

941
00:40:21,619 --> 00:40:25,979
♪Glittering lights all drift away♪

942
00:40:26,060 --> 00:40:30,260
♪Shadows intertwine, row by row♪

943
00:40:30,260 --> 00:40:33,780
♪Endless laughter♪

944
00:40:34,863 --> 00:40:40,823
♪The storm is coming♪

945
00:40:49,340 --> 00:40:52,460
♪The stars sigh♪

946
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:56,300
♪Surrounded by neon lights♪

947
00:40:59,660 --> 00:41:03,900
♪Stacking up dreams
into a sail accidentally♪

948
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:08,420
♪Courage blows the waves off the bay♪

949
00:41:08,420 --> 00:41:12,740
♪Stars ablaze, lights dim and scattered♪

950
00:41:12,740 --> 00:41:17,060
♪Only my lone shadow remains♪

951
00:41:17,500 --> 00:41:20,180
♪This is my fairytale ship♪

952
00:41:37,140 --> 00:41:45,820
♪The evening breeze
stirs restless unease♪

953
00:41:45,820 --> 00:41:51,060
♪Dark clouds scatter across the beach♪

954
00:41:52,780 --> 00:41:57,260
♪The little sailboat secretly departs♪

955
00:41:57,260 --> 00:42:03,340
♪The ocean in the dream remains unseen♪

956
00:42:03,340 --> 00:42:07,500
♪Only waiting♪

957
00:42:07,500 --> 00:42:10,660
♪Fills the distant shore♪

958
00:42:13,420 --> 00:42:17,820
♪Even the stranded light
still feels warm♪

959
00:42:17,820 --> 00:42:22,060
♪Turning into a brighter lighthouse♪

960
00:42:22,060 --> 00:42:26,100
♪It's only another return to shore♪

961
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:30,140
♪No longer lonely♪

962
00:42:31,820 --> 00:42:36,060
♪This is my fairytale ship♪
